```
# Java/Maven specific ignores
target/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Dependencies
lib/
libs/

# Logs
*.log

# IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Build artifacts
build/
dist/
out/

# Python (if mixed project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.venv/
venv/
```